M|Narr|tx|Specify primitive dependencies instead of objects to minimize effect re-runs.
M|Narr|**In|**
M|Narr|tx|```tsx
M|Narr|tx|useEffect(() => {
M|Narr|tx|console.log(us.id)
M|Narr|tx|}, [us])
M|Narr|tx|```
M|Narr|**Co|**
M|Narr|tx|```tsx
M|Narr|tx|useEffect(() => {
M|Narr|tx|console.log(us.id)
M|Narr|tx|}, [us.id])
M|Narr|tx|```
M|Narr|**Fo|**
M|Narr|tx|```tsx
M|Narr|// I|runs on width=767, 766, 765...
M|Narr|tx|useEffect(() => {
M|Narr|tx|if (width < 768) {
M|Narr|tx|enableMobileMode()
M|Narr|tx|}
M|Narr|tx|}, [width])
M|Narr|// C|runs only on boolean transition
M|Narr|tx|const isMobile = width < 768
M|Narr|tx|useEffect(() => {
M|Narr|tx|if (isMobile) {
M|Narr|tx|enableMobileMode()
M|Narr|tx|}
M|Narr|tx|}, [isMobile])
M|Narr|tx|```